<concept id="concept_1E0510B5A3A349049FE82D9894E7DE18"
                    xml:lang="en-us">
        <title>Available Documentation</title>
        <conbody>
                <section>
                        <p>The following documentation on <ph
                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> is available:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                                <li>
                                        <p><i>Overview:</i> A manual introducing <ph
                                                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                        />. It is written for everybody interested in <ph
                                                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                />.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <p><i>Application Operator's Guide:</i> A manual for application operators describing how <ph
                                                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                /> supports them in monitoring their services and virtual machines in OpenStack.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                        <p><i>System Operator's Guide:</i> A manual for system operators describing how to install, operate, and maintain <ph
                                                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                        />. The manual also describes how to prepare the OpenStack platform for <ph
                                                        conref="../product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                                                /> and how to actually use the monitoring functions.</p>
                                </li>
                        </ul>
                </section>
        </conbody>
</concept>
